    8,856 enlisted in Cyprus Regiment (CR)
    1,773 enlisted in Cyprus Volunteer Force (CVF)
    20,000 employed in defence work in Cyprus
    4,500 employed in civil defence services on a compulsory, part-time unpaid basis.


